tasks.details:
PRD mentions 'Chrome extension + cookie proxy' for sites like KREAM and Musinsa. Enhancement needed:

1. Cookie sync mechanism:
   ```javascript
   // extension/background.js
   chrome.cookies.onChanged.addListener(async (changeInfo) => {
     const { cookie, removed, cause } = changeInfo;
     const trackedDomains = ['musinsa.com', 'kream.co.kr', 'lotteon.com'];

     if (trackedDomains.some(d => cookie.domain.includes(d)) && !removed) {
       await syncCookieToBackend(cookie);
     }
   });

   async function syncCookieToBackend(cookie) {
     await fetch(`${API_BASE}/api/v1/samba/sourcing-accounts/cookies`, {
       method: 'POST',
       headers: { 'Authorization': `Bearer ${token}` },
       body: JSON.stringify({
         domain: cookie.domain,
         name: cookie.name,
         value: cookie.value,
         expires: cookie.expirationDate
       })
     });
   }
   ```

2. Backend cookie storage:
   - Encrypt cookies at rest (AES-256)
   - Per-user cookie isolation
   - Automatic expiration handling

3. Cookie injection for API calls:
   - httpx/aiohttp session with custom cookies
   - Automatic refresh when cookies expire
   - Fallback to re-authentication prompt

4. Security considerations:
   - HTTPS only for cookie transmission
   - Rate limit cookie sync endpoints
   - Audit log for cookie access
